1. *Krećem* se ka gradu. (I am moving towards the city.)
2. Zajedno *krećemo* u novu avanturu. (Together we are starting a new adventure.)
3. *Kreni* odmah da završiš zadatke. (Start immediately to finish the tasks.)
4. Moramo *kretati* ranije ako želimo da stignemo na vrijeme. (We have to start earlier if we want to arrive on time.)
5. Jutro se *kreće* polako u ovom dijelu grada. (The morning moves slowly in this part of the city.)
6. Život *kreće* izvan zone komfora. (Life begins outside the comfort zone.)
7. *Kretao* sam se brzo kada sam čuo da me neko prati. (I was moving fast when I heard someone was following me.)
8. Zašto se ne *kreneš* već danas sa učenjem novog jezika? (Why don't you start learning a new language today?)
9. *Kretanje* cijene nafte utiče na globalnu ekonomiju. (The movement of oil prices affects the global economy.)
10. Sunce se *kretalo* prema horizontu dok smo sjedili na plaži. (The sun was moving towards the horizon while we sat on the beach.)